high_descs: Go to the sink, hang a right, go across the room to the garbage can that is on the left.
Pick up the sponge that is in that garbage can.
Go to the fridge that is to the left of the garbage can.
Put the sponge on the white plate inside the fridge.
Pick up the white place that the sponge is on from inside the fridge.
Go to the left to the sink, turn to the left, go forward, turn around and face the cabinets beneath the sink.
Put the plate with the sponge on it inside the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a sponge on it inside a cabinet.

high_descs: go to sink, go right to black bin to the right of refrigerator
pick up green sponge from black bin
go to refrigerator to the left
place green sponge on white plate in refrigerator
pick up white plate with green sponge from top shelf of refrigerator, close refrigerator
turn left, go to cabinet under sink to the right
place white plate with green sponge in cabinet under sink, close cabinet
anns.task_desc: place white plate with green sponge in cabinet under sink

high_descs: Walk forward, then take a right and move to the trash bin to the right of the refrigerator.
Pick up the sponge in the trash bin.
Take a few steps to your left and face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and place the sponge on the plate inside the refrigerator.
Pick up the plate with the sponge on it and close the refrigerator.
Turn left and walk past the kitchen island and face the sink on your right.
Open the cupboard underneath the sink and place the plate with the sponge inside the cupboard, then close the cupboard.
anns.task_desc: Move the sponge in the trash bin on a plate in the refrigerator to the cupboard under the sink.
